<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../298/38298.xml">
George Boole</link></philosopher>
 whose work eventually became one of the foundations of modern computer science, and of surgeon and author <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../312/252312.xml">
James Hinton</link> <weblink xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="http://www.cse.buffalo.edu/~rapaport/111F04/boole.html">
http://www.cse.buffalo.edu/~rapaport/111F04/boole.html</weblink>.</p>

